########################################
# Gmail
########################################

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User xiongchenyu6@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass google.com/xiongchenyu6@gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders Legacy

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "*" 
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All

